*   **Mongolia**: [Mongolian Air Force](/Mongolian_Air_Force) – 4 Su-30SM.
*   **Belarus**: [Belarusian Air Force](/Belarusian_Air_Force) – 8 Su-30SMs and 6 Su-30SM2s in inventory as of December 2025.
*   **Ethiopia**: [Ethiopian Air Force](/Ethiopian_Air_Force) - 2 Su-30K (as of 2024).
*   **India**: [Indian Air Force](/Indian_Air_Force) – 261 Su-30MKI (as of 2024), with an additional 12 ordered in late 2024.
*   **Indonesia**: [Indonesian Air Force](/Indonesian_Air_Force) – 11 Su-30MK2 (as of 2024).
*   **Kazakhstan**: [Kazakh Air Force](/Kazakh_Air_Force) – 29 Su-30SM (as of 2024).
