*   **Russia**:
    *   [Russian Aerospace Forces](/Russian_Aerospace_Forces) – 19 Su-30M2, an estimated 80 Su-30SM, and 4+ Su-30SM2 (as of 2024). New deliveries were conducted in late 2023 and mid-2024.
    *   [Russian Naval Aviation](/Russian_Naval_Aviation) – Approximately 17 Su-30SM and 8+ Su-30SM2 (as of 2024). An additional 2 were delivered in 2025. A total of 50 aircraft are planned.
